com.decoded.zool

Interface ZoolDataBridge

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.zookeeper.AsyncCallback, org.apache.zookeeper.AsyncCallback.StatCallback, org.apache.zookeeper.Watcher
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ZoolDataBridgeImpl

    public interface ZoolDataBridge
extends org.apache.zookeeper.Watcher, org.apache.zookeeper.AsyncCallback.StatCallback
    This represents a connection to a ZooKeeper instance. This extends the Watcher, and the State Callback interfaces, and includes an isDead check for disconnect.
